      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/598961962_18547123033031131_4817612432801220649_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc4NDkxODA5ODMyMzk4MDM3OA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTUyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Oy8bMl_INRIQ7kNvwF9ioPl&amp;_nc_oc=AdqTJC750aqW_JjOXBeD7ze0OESXTnLceuUlyHtH02yG1bThG8IYPIlVTyA_4V2mUTo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=X0E5WbxoK-KfNByGVkWeBQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afx3ikY3zLq7L9duOiU8lSlggcAAJE4cAbjYkECDF5KlKg&amp;oe=69C9BC0B" alt="Instagram billede fra @wildcatebonybrown" /></p><p><strong>@wildcatebonybrown</strong></p><p>Had an amazing out of body experience with Queen @erykahbadu 👑 recently at @kingsbklyn ⚡️Epic show on her Mama’s Gun tour. Thank you Erykah! 🙏💛✨✨✨🌟 Thank you Koko! And thanks to Ernest and team at the beautiful #KingsTheaterBrooklyn 🫶 More to come soon! #erykahbadu #mamasgun</p>]]></description>
